00:00:31.470 --> 00:00:34.830 align:middle line:84%
>> The tradition of knowledge of
the Yuga System is, of course,

00:00:34.830 --> 00:00:39.500 align:middle line:84%
the duration of the yugas and
of the Yuga Cycle in general.

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:42.090 align:middle line:84%
That duration is sort of a
strange figure when you first

00:00:42.090 --> 00:00:47.730 align:middle line:84%
look at it, but it is
precisely 6,048 years.

00:00:47.730 --> 00:00:49.960 align:middle line:84%
As we continue,
we'll see exactly why

00:00:49.960 --> 00:00:53.220 align:middle line:84%
that number emerges as the
key to the entire mystery

00:00:53.220 --> 00:00:55.780 align:middle line:90%
of cyclic time.

00:00:55.780 --> 00:00:59.110 align:middle line:84%
We also learn that the
yugas appear in sets of 10

00:00:59.110 --> 00:01:01.630 align:middle line:84%
and at 10 yugas was
called the Mahakalpa.

00:01:01.630 --> 00:01:05.760 align:middle line:90%


00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:08.700 align:middle line:84%
Thus, we have a
single cycle that

00:01:08.700 --> 00:01:16.800 align:middle line:84%
is a little over 6,000 years
which occurs in sets of 10,

00:01:16.800 --> 00:01:23.930 align:middle line:84%
giving us a roughly
60,000 year cycle overall.

00:01:23.930 --> 00:01:27.700 align:middle line:84%
The first yuga is referred to
as both the Satya or the Krita

00:01:27.700 --> 00:01:29.430 align:middle line:90%
Yuga.

00:01:29.430 --> 00:01:32.610 align:middle line:84%
Krita in Sanskrit means
the Age of Consciousness

00:01:32.610 --> 00:01:34.590 align:middle line:90%
and Accomplishment.

00:01:34.590 --> 00:01:37.590 align:middle line:84%
The Greeks called
this the Golden Age.

00:01:37.590 --> 00:01:40.530 align:middle line:84%
With the metallic
association of the ages,

00:01:40.530 --> 00:01:45.550 align:middle line:84%
we enter a kind of sense
of the alchemy of time.

00:01:45.550 --> 00:01:47.820 align:middle line:84%
The second age is
the age of ritual.

00:01:47.820 --> 00:01:50.100 align:middle line:90%
It's the Treta Yuga.

00:01:50.100 --> 00:01:53.310 align:middle line:84%
In terms of its metallic
value, it is silver.

00:01:53.310 --> 00:01:56.700 align:middle line:84%
And it is in the age
that urbanization began.

00:01:56.700 --> 00:02:00.390 align:middle line:84%
The Treta is called the
Age of the Three Fires.

00:02:00.390 --> 00:02:02.400 align:middle line:84%
The fire was the
fire and smoke that

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:07.810 align:middle line:84%
emerges from the beginning
of dense human settlement

00:02:07.810 --> 00:02:11.280 align:middle line:90%
and the beginning of technology.

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:16.970 align:middle line:84%
The other fires are
the fires of ceremony

00:02:16.970 --> 00:02:21.430 align:middle line:84%
and the fires of the
individual death and cremation.

00:02:21.430 --> 00:02:24.060 align:middle line:84%
As the population
moved and densified,

00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:27.270 align:middle line:84%
new methods of burial began
to emerge that did not

00:02:27.270 --> 00:02:30.400 align:middle line:90%
occupy the former time phases.

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:35.070 align:middle line:84%
This is the age when we see
the beginning of cremation.

00:02:35.070 --> 00:02:37.710 align:middle line:84%
The third age is
called the Dvapara,

00:02:37.710 --> 00:02:39.910 align:middle line:90%
and it means the Age of Doubt.

00:02:39.910 --> 00:02:42.570 align:middle line:90%
It's metal is bronze or copper.

00:02:42.570 --> 00:02:45.690 align:middle line:84%
This is the beginning of a
sensing of the limited duration

00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:48.300 align:middle line:84%
of the whole cyclic
process of the emergence

00:02:48.300 --> 00:02:52.350 align:middle line:84%
of the final and
perfected human form.

00:02:52.350 --> 00:02:55.170 align:middle line:90%
The last is the Age of Kali.

00:02:55.170 --> 00:02:57.310 align:middle line:84%
This is the age in
which there is a mixing

00:02:57.310 --> 00:03:00.360 align:middle line:90%
of the blood of all races.

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:03.150 align:middle line:84%
The last age of Kali
is a concluding age

00:03:03.150 --> 00:03:07.170 align:middle line:90%
in a cycle of 60,480 years.

00:03:07.170 --> 00:03:09.300 align:middle line:84%
This is, of course,
the Iron Age,

00:03:09.300 --> 00:03:13.390 align:middle line:84%
and Kali is the agent of
conflict and destruction.

00:03:13.390 --> 00:03:17.870 align:middle line:10%
The Kali Yuga is 1
times 6,048 years.

00:03:17.870 --> 00:03:25.590 align:middle line:10%
The Dvapara Yuga is 2 times
6,048 years, which is 12,096.

00:03:25.590 --> 00:03:33.550 align:middle line:10%
The Treta Yuga is 3 times
6,048 years, or 18,192 years.

00:03:33.550 --> 00:03:39.120 align:middle line:10%
Then the golden age
is 24,192 years.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:42.160 align:middle line:10%
The setting of our number
system as cycles of 10

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:44.670 align:middle line:10%
is an application to an
understanding of the Yuga

00:03:44.670 --> 00:03:46.140 align:middle line:10%
Cycle.

00:03:46.140 --> 00:03:48.360 align:middle line:84%
There were other
cultures like Babylon

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:51.660 align:middle line:84%
that had a system
based on six and 60.

00:03:51.660 --> 00:03:53.340 align:middle line:84%
But the one that
has sustained itself

00:03:53.340 --> 00:03:57.690 align:middle line:84%
through to the end of the
Kali Yuga is the system of 10.

00:03:57.690 --> 00:04:00.180 align:middle line:84%
We must look at numbers
in terms of each number

00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:04.500 align:middle line:84%
being a fraction of
an original unity.

00:04:04.500 --> 00:04:07.020 align:middle line:90%
Each number then becomes a unit.

00:04:07.020 --> 00:04:11.250 align:middle line:84%
It is an arithmetic progression
with the increase each time

00:04:11.250 --> 00:04:15.240 align:middle line:84%
of one unit like a partitioning
of an overall, all-containing

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:17.010 align:middle line:90%
unity.

00:04:17.010 --> 00:04:19.620 align:middle line:84%
Then we get to the end of the
cycle of the partitioning,

00:04:19.620 --> 00:04:21.720 align:middle line:90%
or division of unity.

00:04:21.720 --> 00:04:26.550 align:middle line:84%
This is the basic container
of its largest scale of time.

00:04:26.550 --> 00:04:29.730 align:middle line:84%
It is very interesting that
10 is a negation of number

00:04:29.730 --> 00:04:34.410 align:middle line:84%
because anything times 0
multiplied with 0 is 0.

00:04:34.410 --> 00:04:37.620 align:middle line:84%
10 is a signal of a
completion and conclusion

00:04:37.620 --> 00:04:40.600 align:middle line:84%
and the end of a
cycle of creation.

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:44.220 align:middle line:84%
This number series reiterates
the basic pattern of time

00:04:44.220 --> 00:04:47.040 align:middle line:84%
and that is especially
applicable to the human being

00:04:47.040 --> 00:04:50.840 align:middle line:84%
who signifies his belonging
to this system of time

00:04:50.840 --> 00:04:54.920 align:middle line:84%
through five fingers, five
toes, and five appendages, two

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:58.740 align:middle line:90%
arms, two legs, and the head.

00:04:58.740 --> 00:05:01.710 align:middle line:84%
The number seven is the
principal and primary unit

00:05:01.710 --> 00:05:05.080 align:middle line:84%
that expresses itself
through the Yuga System.

00:05:05.080 --> 00:05:08.890 align:middle line:84%
The name of the number seven
contains the word even.

00:05:08.890 --> 00:05:14.480 align:middle line:84%
This nomenclature is based on
the fact that 1 times 2 times

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:23.160 align:middle line:84%
3 times 4 times 5 times
6 times 7 equals 5,040.

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:25.460 align:middle line:84%
We have seven, bringing
forth a number that

00:05:25.460 --> 00:05:28.250 align:middle line:84%
is exactly equal to
the radius of the Earth

00:05:28.250 --> 00:05:29.990 align:middle line:90%
and the radius of the moon.

00:05:29.990 --> 00:05:35.780 align:middle line:84%
Then if you continue, we find
that 7 times 8 times 9 times

00:05:35.780 --> 00:05:39.420 align:middle line:90%
10 also equals 5,040.

00:05:39.420 --> 00:05:41.550 align:middle line:84%
So seven is the
break-off point that

00:05:41.550 --> 00:05:45.090 align:middle line:84%
establishes an even
summation, and that summation

00:05:45.090 --> 00:05:48.220 align:middle line:90%
is inherent in the number 10.

00:05:48.220 --> 00:05:52.120 align:middle line:84%
These equations are expressed
by the balance point of seven.

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:55.330 align:middle line:84%
All of it is a reference
to the nature of time.

00:05:55.330 --> 00:05:57.850 align:middle line:84%
Our number system is
based on the entire yuga

00:05:57.850 --> 00:06:00.980 align:middle line:90%
structure of time.

00:06:00.980 --> 00:06:03.740 align:middle line:90%
Also, seven in French is sept.

00:06:03.740 --> 00:06:06.800 align:middle line:84%
And it is the same root sound
that we have in such words

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:12.170 align:middle line:84%
as serpent and Seth, the
Egyptian god of destruction.

00:06:12.170 --> 00:06:17.820 align:middle line:84%
It is a homonym of Set, which
means knowledge and light.

00:06:17.820 --> 00:06:20.370 align:middle line:90%
Set is also the planet Saturn.

00:06:20.370 --> 00:06:22.620 align:middle line:84%
In ancient times,
Saturn was also

00:06:22.620 --> 00:06:26.700 align:middle line:84%
referred to as the seventh
planet and the second sun.

00:06:26.700 --> 00:06:29.820 align:middle line:84%
It could be that there once
was a habitation on a planet

00:06:29.820 --> 00:06:33.420 align:middle line:84%
closer to Saturn whose
energy was creative in terms

00:06:33.420 --> 00:06:35.970 align:middle line:84%
of the processes of
life in the same way

00:06:35.970 --> 00:06:39.810 align:middle line:84%
that the sun is to
our earthly location.

00:06:39.810 --> 00:06:42.690 align:middle line:84%
Indeed, NASA has
reported finding complex,

00:06:42.690 --> 00:06:44.760 align:middle line:84%
organic, and
carbon-based molecules

00:06:44.760 --> 00:06:48.300 align:middle line:84%
on the surface of Titan,
one of Saturn's moons,

00:06:48.300 --> 00:06:52.260 align:middle line:84%
including mass quantities of
methane, ethane, and vinyl

00:06:52.260 --> 00:06:55.410 align:middle line:84%
cyanide, which planetary
scientists theorizes

00:06:55.410 --> 00:06:59.260 align:middle line:84%
similar to Earth's
primordial atmosphere.

00:06:59.260 --> 00:07:02.630 align:middle line:84%
Set in the Egyptian myth
is the villain character

00:07:02.630 --> 00:07:04.490 align:middle line:84%
who brings an end to
the life of Osiris.

00:07:04.490 --> 00:07:08.100 align:middle line:90%


00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:10.890 align:middle line:84%
The name Osiris is
very closely associated

00:07:10.890 --> 00:07:13.630 align:middle line:90%
with the spelling of Sirius.

00:07:13.630 --> 00:07:15.840 align:middle line:84%
Osiris is the
mythic configuration

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:18.810 align:middle line:90%
representing the human species.

00:07:18.810 --> 00:07:21.150 align:middle line:84%
He is the one that
at a certain point

00:07:21.150 --> 00:07:24.600 align:middle line:84%
develops urbanization
and agriculture.

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:28.440 align:middle line:84%
The entire development of Osiris
is an analog to the development

00:07:28.440 --> 00:07:32.420 align:middle line:90%
that man has made on Earth.

00:07:32.420 --> 00:07:36.180 align:middle line:84%
In the golden age, he left
the earth as a Garden of Eden,

00:07:36.180 --> 00:07:40.680 align:middle line:84%
just like what is reiterated in
variation in the Old Testament.

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:44.160 align:middle line:84%
Later, he set himself into
a life of constant labor

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:46.030 align:middle line:90%
through agriculture.

00:07:46.030 --> 00:07:48.345 align:middle line:84%
This is all reiterated
in the myth of Osiris.

00:07:48.345 --> 00:07:51.100 align:middle line:90%


00:07:51.100 --> 00:07:54.850 align:middle line:84%
Set, related to seven, is
both the mother and destroyer

00:07:54.850 --> 00:07:57.580 align:middle line:84%
of the proportions of
the Earth and moon, which

00:07:57.580 --> 00:08:00.790 align:middle line:84%
are of critical importance to
generating the vibration which

00:08:00.790 --> 00:08:02.890 align:middle line:84%
allows substance to
become conscious.

00:08:02.890 --> 00:08:05.670 align:middle line:90%


00:08:05.670 --> 00:08:07.680 align:middle line:84%
Another important
point mentioned

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:11.100 align:middle line:84%
was the relationship between the
timing of the birth of Buddha

00:08:11.100 --> 00:08:15.090 align:middle line:84%
and the birth of Christ and
that the Puranas specifically

00:08:15.090 --> 00:08:18.030 align:middle line:84%
say that Buddha is the
avatar of the Kali Yuga.

00:08:18.030 --> 00:08:21.140 align:middle line:90%


00:08:21.140 --> 00:08:23.990 align:middle line:84%
Information from several
of the Puranic texts

00:08:23.990 --> 00:08:25.880 align:middle line:84%
tell us that the
teachings of Buddha

00:08:25.880 --> 00:08:29.120 align:middle line:84%
contain the formula for the
transformation of consciousness

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.520 align:middle line:90%
into a sense of individuality.

00:08:32.520 --> 00:08:34.630 align:middle line:84%
It's a teaching of
rising above the ego

00:08:34.630 --> 00:08:37.250 align:middle line:90%
to the true individual self.

00:08:37.250 --> 00:08:39.770 align:middle line:84%
This teaching in
its deformed state

00:08:39.770 --> 00:08:41.929 align:middle line:84%
became a sense of
self-realization

00:08:41.929 --> 00:08:44.870 align:middle line:84%
and self-righteousness
not on the spiritual,

00:08:44.870 --> 00:08:47.000 align:middle line:84%
but on the material
sense and led

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:50.000 align:middle line:84%
to the whole idea of
realization through accumulation

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:51.860 align:middle line:90%
of wealth and power.

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:54.680 align:middle line:84%
That teaching in its lower
form became the theory

00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:57.410 align:middle line:84%
of capitalism, the
role of the individual

00:08:57.410 --> 00:09:01.370 align:middle line:84%
and is consuming, acquiring,
and acquisitive processes, which

00:09:01.370 --> 00:09:03.470 align:middle line:84%
were a huge
enhancement to commerce

00:09:03.470 --> 00:09:05.480 align:middle line:84%
and allowed the whole
of the Kali Yuga

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:08.780 align:middle line:84%
to be dominated by
the commercial caste.

00:09:08.780 --> 00:09:13.260 align:middle line:84%
This is not in any way a
derogatory view of Buddhism.

00:09:13.260 --> 00:09:15.370 align:middle line:84%
Buddhism is an
ingenious creation

00:09:15.370 --> 00:09:18.350 align:middle line:84%
that hastened and assured
the direction or termination

00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:20.690 align:middle line:84%
of this phase of our
development in terms

00:09:20.690 --> 00:09:23.750 align:middle line:84%
of the prescribed
directives of time.

00:09:23.750 --> 00:09:26.810 align:middle line:84%
Buddha was actually fulfilling
the harmonics of the duration

00:09:26.810 --> 00:09:28.490 align:middle line:90%
of the Kali Yuga.

00:09:28.490 --> 00:09:30.890 align:middle line:84%
The remarkable aspect
of his teachings

00:09:30.890 --> 00:09:33.470 align:middle line:84%
is that it brings about the
destructive attitudes that

00:09:33.470 --> 00:09:35.750 align:middle line:84%
lead to the destruction
of the Earth

00:09:35.750 --> 00:09:39.990 align:middle line:84%
through our almost insane
obsession with consumption.

00:09:39.990 --> 00:09:41.720 align:middle line:84%
He also gave a
formula, which would

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:44.960 align:middle line:84%
allow people who are aware of
and sensitive to the nature

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:49.130 align:middle line:84%
of time to be able to
confront this direction.

00:09:49.130 --> 00:09:52.490 align:middle line:84%
That is the detachment, the
argument that this material

00:09:52.490 --> 00:09:55.310 align:middle line:90%
world is only an illusion.

00:09:55.310 --> 00:09:57.770 align:middle line:84%
This fortified the ability
to confront and face

00:09:57.770 --> 00:10:01.520 align:middle line:84%
the disillusion with courage
and a kind of dignity.

00:10:01.520 --> 00:10:03.380 align:middle line:84%
Those are several
major points that

00:10:03.380 --> 00:10:05.630 align:middle line:84%
continue to draw
upon and reinforce

00:10:05.630 --> 00:10:08.900 align:middle line:84%
the symbolism and the
possible accuracy of this very

00:10:08.900 --> 00:10:11.660 align:middle line:90%
ancient prophetic system.

00:10:11.660 --> 00:10:15.170 align:middle line:10%
Let's examine the idea of how
the human organism is embedded

00:10:15.170 --> 00:10:18.440 align:middle line:10%
in the cyclic processes
and pulsations of time

00:10:18.440 --> 00:10:20.720 align:middle line:10%
within the entire
vast cycles of time

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:25.050 align:middle line:10%
called the yugas and the
procession of the equinox.

00:10:25.050 --> 00:10:28.330 align:middle line:10%
Our breathing and our
heartbeat are time intervals

00:10:28.330 --> 00:10:30.200 align:middle line:10%
that are resonant
within the pulsation

00:10:30.200 --> 00:10:32.330 align:middle line:10%
and patterns of the Earth.

00:10:32.330 --> 00:10:35.990 align:middle line:84%
For example, the human breath,
a normal full inhalation

00:10:35.990 --> 00:10:39.890 align:middle line:84%
and exhalation, if it's not
cramped or reduced or repressed

00:10:39.890 --> 00:10:44.210 align:middle line:84%
by nervous tension, requires
four seconds of time.

00:10:44.210 --> 00:10:48.050 align:middle line:84%
60 of these breaths, or pranas,
as they're called in India,

00:10:48.050 --> 00:10:50.450 align:middle line:84%
is equal to the time
necessary for the Earth

00:10:50.450 --> 00:10:54.210 align:middle line:90%
to rotate one degree.

00:10:54.210 --> 00:10:56.510 align:middle line:84%
Another interesting
statistic is that

00:10:56.510 --> 00:10:59.420 align:middle line:84%
in a complete sidereal
day, a human being

00:10:59.420 --> 00:11:03.610 align:middle line:90%
should breathe 21,600 breaths.

00:11:03.610 --> 00:11:08.030 align:middle line:84%
A harmonic of this
number 2,160 is of course

00:11:08.030 --> 00:11:11.580 align:middle line:84%
the duration of years in
one sign of the zodiac

00:11:11.580 --> 00:11:14.315 align:middle line:84%
and is the measurement of the
diameter of the moon in miles.

00:11:14.315 --> 00:11:16.850 align:middle line:90%


00:11:16.850 --> 00:11:22.610 align:middle line:84%
In ancient times, the fathom is
a length of both arms extended.

00:11:22.610 --> 00:11:25.490 align:middle line:84%
Using Egyptian measures,
we find that a sphere

00:11:25.490 --> 00:11:29.330 align:middle line:84%
with the circumference
measuring 21,600,000 arms

00:11:29.330 --> 00:11:33.680 align:middle line:84%
spans, or fathoms, is
a close approximation

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:35.000 align:middle line:90%
of the equator of the Earth.

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:40.150 align:middle line:90%


00:11:40.150 --> 00:11:42.610 align:middle line:84%
The Earth's polar ice
cap, which comes down

00:11:42.610 --> 00:11:47.035 align:middle line:84%
to the 74th or 75th
latitude, is frozen ice.

00:11:47.035 --> 00:11:49.600 align:middle line:84%
And this is in
proportion to the globe

00:11:49.600 --> 00:11:52.330 align:middle line:84%
equals the proportion of
what the Egyptians called

00:11:52.330 --> 00:11:56.270 align:middle line:84%
the skullcap, which encloses
the cerebral cortex.

00:11:56.270 --> 00:11:57.760 align:middle line:84%
This is the part
of the brain that

00:11:57.760 --> 00:12:00.280 align:middle line:84%
has undergone tremendous
neurological changes

00:12:00.280 --> 00:12:03.580 align:middle line:84%
during the Kali Yuga,
especially in response

00:12:03.580 --> 00:12:06.355 align:middle line:84%
to the great drought that began
at the beginning of the Kali

00:12:06.355 --> 00:12:08.570 align:middle line:90%
Yuga.

00:12:08.570 --> 00:12:11.000 align:middle line:84%
Archeologists have
verified the time period

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:13.610 align:middle line:84%
we've chosen as the
beginning of the Kali Yuga.

00:12:13.610 --> 00:12:17.960 align:middle line:84%
3606 BC is a close
approximation to the beginning

00:12:17.960 --> 00:12:21.260 align:middle line:84%
of the drying that caused
the Middle East, the Iranian

00:12:21.260 --> 00:12:24.530 align:middle line:84%
Plateau, Arabia,
and Northern Africa

00:12:24.530 --> 00:12:28.730 align:middle line:84%
to go into a sudden
reduction of rainfall.

00:12:28.730 --> 00:12:31.730 align:middle line:84%
This drought affected
security and a sense of life

00:12:31.730 --> 00:12:35.200 align:middle line:90%
and induced the fear of hunger.

