Starvation caused the beginning
of refugee populations, people

00:12:39.190 --> 00:12:41.290 align:middle line:84%
breaking connection with
the lands of their birth

00:12:41.290 --> 00:12:45.100 align:middle line:84%
and moving around, not
necessarily nomadically,

00:12:45.100 --> 00:12:49.270 align:middle line:84%
but searching for places
to settle and resettle.

00:12:49.270 --> 00:12:52.780 align:middle line:84%
In our examination of the human
body, moving from the skullcap

00:12:52.780 --> 00:12:55.030 align:middle line:84%
to the hand and
finger, we find this

00:12:55.030 --> 00:12:57.400 align:middle line:84%
is the key to understanding
the entire system

00:12:57.400 --> 00:12:59.440 align:middle line:90%
of Egyptian measure.

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:02.230 align:middle line:84%
And all of these measures
are relative to the forms

00:13:02.230 --> 00:13:04.140 align:middle line:90%
and structures of the Earth.

00:13:04.140 --> 00:13:08.410 align:middle line:84%
With Egyptian measure, the
width of a finger is a digit.

00:13:08.410 --> 00:13:11.530 align:middle line:90%
Four digits is a palm.

00:13:11.530 --> 00:13:16.110 align:middle line:84%
And seven palms of four
digits is a royal cubit.

00:13:16.110 --> 00:13:18.970 align:middle line:84%
A cubit can also be measured
from the extended hand

00:13:18.970 --> 00:13:20.980 align:middle line:90%
to the elbow.

00:13:20.980 --> 00:13:23.290 align:middle line:10%
Let's look to the crown
of the skull, which

00:13:23.290 --> 00:13:26.200 align:middle line:10%
is a big focus point in
terms of the Egyptian view

00:13:26.200 --> 00:13:28.000 align:middle line:10%
of human evolution.

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:30.760 align:middle line:84%
And, remember, this
skullcap is symbolized

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:34.360 align:middle line:90%
by the scarab in Egypt.

00:13:34.360 --> 00:13:37.240 align:middle line:84%
If you place the palm of the
hand at the top of your head,

00:13:37.240 --> 00:13:40.840 align:middle line:84%
you get the exact measure
of the crown of the skull.

00:13:40.840 --> 00:13:43.150 align:middle line:90%
Its size is one palm.

00:13:43.150 --> 00:13:46.480 align:middle line:84%
Then if you count three
palms down, or 12 fingers,

00:13:46.480 --> 00:13:48.280 align:middle line:90%
you get to the jaw.

00:13:48.280 --> 00:13:50.020 align:middle line:84%
And the whole
capacity for speech

00:13:50.020 --> 00:13:51.430 align:middle line:90%
is contained in that palm.

00:13:51.430 --> 00:13:54.040 align:middle line:90%


00:13:54.040 --> 00:13:57.460 align:middle line:10%
Then you go underneath, and
the fourth palm of four digits

00:13:57.460 --> 00:14:00.820 align:middle line:10%
reaches the voice box, which
allows for the articulation

00:14:00.820 --> 00:14:03.160 align:middle line:10%
of language.

00:14:03.160 --> 00:14:05.680 align:middle line:84%
The conception to the
articulation processes

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:10.000 align:middle line:84%
of a human being are found
in the first four palms.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:12.100 align:middle line:84%
This is the genius
of Egypt, the way

00:14:12.100 --> 00:14:15.380 align:middle line:84%
they understood the relationship
between man and Earth.

00:14:15.380 --> 00:14:18.280 align:middle line:90%


00:14:18.280 --> 00:14:21.190 align:middle line:10%
Schwaller de Lubicz,
the great Egyptologist,

00:14:21.190 --> 00:14:25.030 align:middle line:10%
said that the Egyptians really
believed in the anthropocosm

00:14:25.030 --> 00:14:27.640 align:middle line:10%
that the measures and
proportions of the human body

00:14:27.640 --> 00:14:29.620 align:middle line:10%
contained the
significant dimensions

00:14:29.620 --> 00:14:32.980 align:middle line:10%
of the entire universe.

00:14:32.980 --> 00:14:36.070 align:middle line:84%
Let's review some of the
astronomical associations

00:14:36.070 --> 00:14:39.750 align:middle line:90%
with the proportion of 18.618.

00:14:39.750 --> 00:14:42.190 align:middle line:84%
This is actually a
golden mean number,

00:14:42.190 --> 00:14:45.790 align:middle line:90%
as it is 18 plus 1 over phi.

00:14:45.790 --> 00:14:51.280 align:middle line:84%
The square of this number,
18.618 times 18.618,

00:14:51.280 --> 00:14:53.140 align:middle line:84%
is the number of
days in an eclipse

00:14:53.140 --> 00:14:58.140 align:middle line:90%
year, which is 346.62 days.

00:14:58.140 --> 00:15:00.520 align:middle line:84%
An eclipse year is
calculated as the number

00:15:00.520 --> 00:15:04.000 align:middle line:84%
of days between two successive
conjunctions of the sun

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:06.940 align:middle line:84%
with the same node
of the moon's orbit.

00:15:06.940 --> 00:15:11.050 align:middle line:84%
The moon is positioned and is
of the exact size necessary so

00:15:11.050 --> 00:15:14.120 align:middle line:84%
that at an eclipse,
it completely

00:15:14.120 --> 00:15:17.960 align:middle line:84%
covers the sun, which is
93 million miles away.

00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:21.030 align:middle line:90%


00:15:21.030 --> 00:15:25.250 align:middle line:84%
The sun is approximately 400
times larger than the moon.

00:15:25.250 --> 00:15:28.310 align:middle line:10%
The moon is nearly
1/400 the distance

00:15:28.310 --> 00:15:31.120 align:middle line:10%
between the Earth and the sun.

00:15:31.120 --> 00:15:33.160 align:middle line:84%
Because of this
amazing coincidence,

00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:36.070 align:middle line:84%
the moon perfectly covers
the sun in a total eclipse.

00:15:36.070 --> 00:15:39.380 align:middle line:90%


00:15:39.380 --> 00:15:45.500 align:middle line:84%
In addition to the eclipse
year, 18.618 times 19.618

00:15:45.500 --> 00:15:52.220 align:middle line:84%
equals 365.25, which is
exactly the solar year.

00:15:52.220 --> 00:15:59.400 align:middle line:84%
18.618 times 20.168
is 383.89 days,

00:15:59.400 --> 00:16:01.820 align:middle line:84%
which is the exact
duration of 13 lunar

00:16:01.820 --> 00:16:06.530 align:middle line:90%
cycles of 29.5 days each.

00:16:06.530 --> 00:16:09.800 align:middle line:10%
The more you allow yourself to
examine the geometry of time

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:13.670 align:middle line:10%
and space, the more the ideas
that this process which we're

00:16:13.670 --> 00:16:16.400 align:middle line:10%
in is based on
chance or probability

00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:18.350 align:middle line:10%
and those whole
concepts which dominate

00:16:18.350 --> 00:16:23.300 align:middle line:10%
the Darwinian idea of evolution
become completely absurd.

00:16:23.300 --> 00:16:26.300 align:middle line:84%
It's either childish
notions or it's fabricated.

00:16:26.300 --> 00:16:31.300 align:middle line:84%
In other words,
intentional disinformation.

00:16:31.300 --> 00:16:34.450 align:middle line:84%
The total human body's height
contains approximately seven

00:16:34.450 --> 00:16:36.100 align:middle line:90%
heads in total.

00:16:36.100 --> 00:16:39.250 align:middle line:84%
Women are almost exactly
seven heads in height,

00:16:39.250 --> 00:16:42.670 align:middle line:84%
while men tend to be 7
and 1/2 heads in height.

00:16:42.670 --> 00:16:44.530 align:middle line:84%
But with careful
measurement, as far

00:16:44.530 --> 00:16:46.520 align:middle line:84%
as the height of
an average woman,

00:16:46.520 --> 00:16:52.380 align:middle line:84%
you will find that it is not
just 7, but it is 7.142 heads.

00:16:52.380 --> 00:16:53.860 align:middle line:90%
It's not a whole number.

00:16:53.860 --> 00:16:56.700 align:middle line:84%
It's an irrational number,
a continuous decimal

00:16:56.700 --> 00:16:59.900 align:middle line:90%
into infinity.

00:16:59.900 --> 00:17:02.630 align:middle line:84%
Not only is the human
body using seven heads

00:17:02.630 --> 00:17:06.260 align:middle line:84%
to describe its height, it
also has seven meridian points

00:17:06.260 --> 00:17:08.210 align:middle line:84%
running up and
down the human body

00:17:08.210 --> 00:17:10.220 align:middle line:84%
as the subtle centers
of energy that

00:17:10.220 --> 00:17:13.220 align:middle line:90%
emanate from the seven chakras.

00:17:13.220 --> 00:17:15.930 align:middle line:84%
To the left and to the
right are the energies

00:17:15.930 --> 00:17:18.500 align:middle line:84%
that from the meridians
extend and emanate

00:17:18.500 --> 00:17:20.869 align:middle line:84%
into the field that
surrounds the body, which

00:17:20.869 --> 00:17:22.504 align:middle line:90%
the Egyptians called the ka.

00:17:22.504 --> 00:17:26.680 align:middle line:90%


00:17:26.680 --> 00:17:29.660 align:middle line:90%
We are this 14th part of 1,000.

00:17:29.660 --> 00:17:32.800 align:middle line:84%
What 1,000 represents
in Indian thought

00:17:32.800 --> 00:17:35.380 align:middle line:90%
is three levels of existence.

00:17:35.380 --> 00:17:37.840 align:middle line:84%
We saw 10 as the
number of the divisions

00:17:37.840 --> 00:17:40.150 align:middle line:84%
that unity makes to
create the harmonics

00:17:40.150 --> 00:17:43.630 align:middle line:84%
in the vibratory world, which
leads to all these harmonics

00:17:43.630 --> 00:17:45.920 align:middle line:90%
within the formal world.

00:17:45.920 --> 00:17:49.820 align:middle line:84%
Seven and 14 are the number of
fields that are generated back

00:17:49.820 --> 00:17:52.400 align:middle line:90%
into the vibratory environment.

00:17:52.400 --> 00:17:55.580 align:middle line:84%
We can begin to see the
entire process of embodiment

00:17:55.580 --> 00:17:58.730 align:middle line:84%
by understanding its resonance
with certain configurations

00:17:58.730 --> 00:18:00.360 align:middle line:90%
of time.

00:18:00.360 --> 00:18:02.540 align:middle line:84%
This is the process in
which the energy goes

00:18:02.540 --> 00:18:07.220 align:middle line:84%
from an energetic state into an
embodied or substantiated state

00:18:07.220 --> 00:18:09.020 align:middle line:90%
and then back again.

00:18:09.020 --> 00:18:12.380 align:middle line:84%
It is sustained physiologically
with the constant composing

00:18:12.380 --> 00:18:15.080 align:middle line:90%
and decomposing of tissue.

00:18:15.080 --> 00:18:17.810 align:middle line:84%
It is a process that
causes an emanation,

00:18:17.810 --> 00:18:21.440 align:middle line:84%
and that decomposed substance
emanates itself resonantly back

00:18:21.440 --> 00:18:23.630 align:middle line:90%
into a field.

00:18:23.630 --> 00:18:27.110 align:middle line:84%
Life and embodiment is
moving from a wave situation

00:18:27.110 --> 00:18:32.450 align:middle line:84%
to a particle structure as they
have found in quantum theory.

00:18:32.450 --> 00:18:37.950 align:middle line:84%
From particle to wave and
from wave into particle,

00:18:37.950 --> 00:18:41.340 align:middle line:84%
this is the succession
of matter from waveform

00:18:41.340 --> 00:18:44.140 align:middle line:90%
to form and back again.

00:18:44.140 --> 00:18:49.400 align:middle line:90%


00:18:49.400 --> 00:18:52.700 align:middle line:84%
The texts that are supposedly
the most authentic concerning

00:18:52.700 --> 00:18:56.000 align:middle line:84%
the life of Buddha are
found in Tibet and India,

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:59.990 align:middle line:84%
particularly the texts
found in Sri Lanka.

00:18:59.990 --> 00:19:05.120 align:middle line:84%
They say that Buddha lived
for 78 years, born in 621 BC,

00:19:05.120 --> 00:19:07.700 align:middle line:90%
and died in 543 BC.

00:19:07.700 --> 00:19:10.880 align:middle line:90%
That's a duration of 78 years.

00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:13.130 align:middle line:10%
His realization is
said to have occurred,

00:19:13.130 --> 00:19:17.330 align:middle line:10%
as the same with Christ,
when he was 33 years old.

00:19:17.330 --> 00:19:20.130 align:middle line:10%
That occurs in the
midpoint of his life.

00:19:20.130 --> 00:19:22.070 align:middle line:10%
That means that the
midpoint of his life

00:19:22.070 --> 00:19:25.010 align:middle line:10%
and his spiritual
realization is exactly

00:19:25.010 --> 00:19:30.530 align:middle line:10%
at 582 BC, the very
center of the Kali Yuga.

00:19:30.530 --> 00:19:33.230 align:middle line:84%
Buddha was born in the
age of Aries, which is

00:19:33.230 --> 00:19:35.510 align:middle line:90%
the first sign of the zodiac.

00:19:35.510 --> 00:19:39.740 align:middle line:84%
In approximately 150 BC, we
change from the sign of Aries

00:19:39.740 --> 00:19:41.510 align:middle line:90%
to the sign of Pisces.

00:19:41.510 --> 00:19:45.560 align:middle line:84%
Thus, we have 432 years
separating the birth of Buddha

00:19:45.560 --> 00:19:48.080 align:middle line:84%
from the beginning
of the age of Pisces.

00:19:48.080 --> 00:19:52.280 align:middle line:84%
And, as we have seen, 432 is
one of the major multiples

00:19:52.280 --> 00:19:54.650 align:middle line:90%
of the procession.

00:19:54.650 --> 00:19:57.500 align:middle line:84%
The Puranas prophesied
that amongst the barbarians

00:19:57.500 --> 00:20:01.220 align:middle line:84%
of the West, an avatar who is
simply an extension of Buddha

00:20:01.220 --> 00:20:02.750 align:middle line:90%
would arise.

00:20:02.750 --> 00:20:05.360 align:middle line:84%
Many people have interpreted
that the second phase

00:20:05.360 --> 00:20:09.080 align:middle line:84%
of the avatar of
Buddha is Christ.

00:20:09.080 --> 00:20:12.380 align:middle line:84%
Let's take a look at the
key dates concerning Christ.

00:20:12.380 --> 00:20:16.850 align:middle line:84%
It appears that the birth of
Christ was either 3 or 4 AD.

00:20:16.850 --> 00:20:20.300 align:middle line:84%
This means that he was
born in the age of Pisces.

00:20:20.300 --> 00:20:22.280 align:middle line:84%
There is much medieval
symbolism which

00:20:22.280 --> 00:20:25.520 align:middle line:84%
associates Christ as the
dominant figure of the Piscean

00:20:25.520 --> 00:20:26.750 align:middle line:90%
Age.

00:20:26.750 --> 00:20:28.520 align:middle line:84%
It's very interesting
that Buddha

00:20:28.520 --> 00:20:31.730 align:middle line:84%
is the dominant figure
coming from the age of Aries

00:20:31.730 --> 00:20:36.590 align:middle line:84%
and Christ is the dominant
figure of the Piscean Age.

00:20:36.590 --> 00:20:38.750 align:middle line:84%
Christ was said to
have his realization

00:20:38.750 --> 00:20:43.010 align:middle line:84%
through a sacrificial ritual
33 years after year 4,

00:20:43.010 --> 00:20:45.620 align:middle line:90%
which would make it 37 AD.

00:20:45.620 --> 00:20:49.470 align:middle line:84%
The sacrificial ritual was
the Resurrection of Christ.

00:20:49.470 --> 00:20:53.810 align:middle line:84%
This begins a series of numbers
based on the intervals of 37.

00:20:53.810 --> 00:20:56.990 align:middle line:84%
This is again three and
seven, the key numbers

00:20:56.990 --> 00:21:00.890 align:middle line:84%
in the merger of the precession
with the Yuga System.

00:21:00.890 --> 00:21:05.000 align:middle line:84%
All of the dates then in
this yuga can start with 37.

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:07.970 align:middle line:84%
37 is a very interesting
number because it

00:21:07.970 --> 00:21:11.030 align:middle line:84%
is what we call the
number of the triplicity.

00:21:11.030 --> 00:21:16.190 align:middle line:84%
Every time you multiply a 2
or a multiple of 3 times 37,

00:21:16.190 --> 00:21:18.260 align:middle line:90%
you get a triple number.

00:21:18.260 --> 00:21:23.520 align:middle line:90%
3 times 37 is 111.

00:21:23.520 --> 00:21:28.770 align:middle line:90%
6 times 37 is 222.

00:21:28.770 --> 00:21:31.100 align:middle line:84%
This triplicity
continues all the way

00:21:31.100 --> 00:21:36.590 align:middle line:84%
through the number 999,
which is 37 times 27.

00:21:36.590 --> 00:21:40.400 align:middle line:84%
Additionally, we can
follow the succession of 37

00:21:40.400 --> 00:21:43.100 align:middle line:84%
up to the date of the end
of the Kali Yuga, which

00:21:43.100 --> 00:21:49.160 align:middle line:90%
is 37 times 66, or 2,444.

00:21:49.160 --> 00:21:51.380 align:middle line:10%
It's one of the more
interesting explorations

00:21:51.380 --> 00:21:53.750 align:middle line:10%
of the symbolic
nature of our history

00:21:53.750 --> 00:21:56.840 align:middle line:10%
to go through the
multiples of 37.

00:21:56.840 --> 00:21:59.180 align:middle line:84%
One of the most prominent
and most interesting

00:21:59.180 --> 00:22:01.370 align:middle line:84%
will be the appearance
of the United States

00:22:01.370 --> 00:22:04.270 align:middle line:90%
and the origins of that country.

00:22:04.270 --> 00:22:09.190 align:middle line:10%
1776 is a multiple
of 37 times 48, which

00:22:09.190 --> 00:22:11.410 align:middle line:10%
is the number of states
in the first completed

00:22:11.410 --> 00:22:14.140 align:middle line:10%
union of the United States.

00:22:14.140 --> 00:22:16.780 align:middle line:10%
It is also the birthday
of the politically active

00:22:16.780 --> 00:22:18.490 align:middle line:10%
and historically
formative secret

00:22:18.490 --> 00:22:22.000 align:middle line:10%
society known as the Illuminati.

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:24.040 align:middle line:10%
The Illuminati was
started by a Jesuit

00:22:24.040 --> 00:22:27.280 align:middle line:10%
priest named Adam Weishaupt.

00:22:27.280 --> 00:22:28.870 align:middle line:10%
There is ample
evidence that he was

00:22:28.870 --> 00:22:31.240 align:middle line:10%
a main influence on
Benjamin Franklin

00:22:31.240 --> 00:22:34.630 align:middle line:10%
and the founders of the United
States, even to the degree

00:22:34.630 --> 00:22:39.230 align:middle line:10%
that the Washington Monument
is exactly 555 feet high,

00:22:39.230 --> 00:22:42.130 align:middle line:10%
which is 15 times 37.

00:22:42.130 --> 00:22:44.530 align:middle line:84%
The entire street
design of Washington

00:22:44.530 --> 00:22:47.830 align:middle line:84%
is based on an angle
of 72 degrees, which

00:22:47.830 --> 00:22:50.650 align:middle line:90%
is descriptive of a Pentagon.

00:22:50.650 --> 00:22:53.800 align:middle line:84%
We will get to the Pentagon
and its importance in the yuga

00:22:53.800 --> 00:22:58.090 align:middle line:84%
and in the story of
mankind in later episodes.

00:22:58.090 --> 00:23:01.610 align:middle line:84%
All these numbers
are multiples of 37.

00:23:01.610 --> 00:23:05.820 align:middle line:84%
The year 1665, which is
the great plague of London,

00:23:05.820 --> 00:23:08.970 align:middle line:90%
is 37 times 45.

00:23:08.970 --> 00:23:13.410 align:middle line:84%
The year 1998, which
is 37 times 54,

00:23:13.410 --> 00:23:15.810 align:middle line:84%
is when the sun returned
to direct alignment

00:23:15.810 --> 00:23:18.390 align:middle line:90%
with the center of the galaxy.

00:23:18.390 --> 00:23:21.480 align:middle line:84%
All of these are yuga dates
set by the resurrection

00:23:21.480 --> 00:23:23.460 align:middle line:90%
of the body of Christ.

00:23:23.460 --> 00:23:26.130 align:middle line:84%
Christ, his death
and resurrection,

00:23:26.130 --> 00:23:28.560 align:middle line:84%
is the symbol for the
Kali Yuga's potential

00:23:28.560 --> 00:23:31.590 align:middle line:84%
for the death and resurrection
of the entire body

00:23:31.590 --> 00:23:34.740 align:middle line:90%
of the human species.

00:23:34.740 --> 00:23:37.710 align:middle line:84%
In this way, we can see
that the Buddha taught

00:23:37.710 --> 00:23:40.110 align:middle line:84%
us to meditate and
accept the coming

00:23:40.110 --> 00:23:45.180 align:middle line:84%
destruction of ourselves, both
as a body and as a species,

00:23:45.180 --> 00:23:46.980 align:middle line:84%
while the teachings
of Christ were

00:23:46.980 --> 00:23:50.670 align:middle line:84%
to show us that a resurrection
of the body and of the species

00:23:50.670 --> 00:23:53.820 align:middle line:90%
is absolutely possible.

00:23:53.820 --> 00:23:57.990 align:middle line:84%
Both Buddha and Jesus Christ,
avatars of the Kali Yuga,

00:23:57.990 --> 00:24:00.450 align:middle line:84%
gave our species
knowledge and tools

00:24:00.450 --> 00:24:03.060 align:middle line:84%
that will help us endure
the destructive tendencies

00:24:03.060 --> 00:24:04.290 align:middle line:90%
of our age.

